data.description: Holiday Special! Seller will pay up to $10k in closing cost, prepaids and rate buy down. From the moment you enter this beautiful space you will feel like you're at home. Upon entering you'll notice an open concept layout leading into the living room, the sun beaming in is just the warmth you'll be looking for on cooler days. Leading into the kitchen you'll find stainless steel appliances and plenty of room for a table. The walk-in pantry offers ample storage. Next is a recently updated powder room and a main floor laundry room w/addl. storage. Upstairs you'll find the main bedroom with a spacious walk-in closet with a full bathroom, also 3 more bedrooms along with a full bathroom. Now for the basement! Brand new space for all your needs. You'll find an open area for entertaining, a full bath and a spacious bedroom/office with a walk-in closet. Don't forget to check out the large expansive fenced in backyard with a large maintenance free deck over looking the above ground pool.
